{
  "stem": "20088.9",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mother went to Professor-- he was Professor Koenig, the headmaster-- and asked him if I would get free the afternoons to go to that studio.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, well, I must have a medical certificate that I could physically cope with that after all I'd been through at the camp, and you know, it might be a lot of strain.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He actually advised against it, but I wanted to do it, and my mother said I had to do it, so.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I had a medical certificate, and I also had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I must say, after the war I had lot of trouble with my digestion.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was for about two years.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was on a strict diet, just noodles and semolina and dry potatoes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't eat anything else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Partly perhaps it was because I had overeaten too much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that went on for many years and a very nervous stomach.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had diarrhea as soon as I had an exam or anything like that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But after a few years, that passed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And at this studio, there was a customer who had been to Spain.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had taken hundreds of photographs, but he had never printed them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said to my boss, is there perhaps somebody who could work in the evening and print-- I've got all the equipment-- and print all those photographs for me?",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll pay, of course.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- and so he asked me if I want to do that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I said, yes, I'll do that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So after work, I went home first, to eat, and then I went on the bicycle in the night to this man, who was quite far again.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I worked a few hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I printed perhaps three, four, at least, printing.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
